title: Under Pete Carroll, Seahawks nearly perfect in prime time
text: > Washington Under Pete Carroll, Seahawks nearly perfect in prime time FILE - In this Aug. 29, 2015, file photo, Seattle Seahawks head coach Pete Carroll yells to his team during the second half of a preseason NFL football game against the San Diego Chargers in San Diego. As part of the program he has constructed in Seattle, Pete Carroll insists that all games are equal and those with higher profiles carry no extra significance.
